I have lived in several aprtments and this one by far takes the rotten slice of cake. My year lease is up in December&#44; and I WILL NOT be renewing my lease. When my friends mention apartment hunting&#44; I tell them to run far FAR away from mine. Yes&#44; it looks sort of nice. They just got the winter grass planted again so it no longer looks like a waste land&#44; but it by no means is enough to keep me here a day longer than I have to. Safe environment? No. My car has been keyed several times along with many other cars. Some kids have been going around shoving nails in tires. A man has come up to me and licked&#44; yes you read right&#44; LICKED my face while I was checkin my mail and unnaware of his approach. My car battery died and I was seraching through my glove box looking for my warranty papers when two guys who were clearly on something came up and was &#34;hollerin&#34; at me and when I shut and locked my door out of annoyance they ran up to my car and started punching my windows yelling &#34;you -----!&#34; while my neighbor watched on. Security?? what security? Yeah I&#39;ve seen em around but theyre so scrawny and nerdy looking I&#39;m sure they couldnt hurt a fly. Besides&#44; all they do is ride their bikes around at night day dreaming. The people in the office are complete imbociles. When I reported all of this each time all they did was laugh and say &#34;I guess we&#39;re not getting the fence up fast enough!&#34; ha. ha. I have been battling with them over a roach problem almost a year now. I don&#39;t even have a single crumb of food in my house. I threw it all away months ago. I&#39;ve suposively been sprayed 4 times&#44; although I&#39;ve only witnessed the one spraying&#44; and before he left I had to stop him and walk through the apartment showing him where to spray because he spent a whole 4 minutes doing a half --- job. The people down stairs have at least 8 people living in their one bedroom apartment. And their 2 year old girl dumps food and milk and soda and juice EVERYWHERE outside. It smelled like sour milk for weeks. I&#39;ll come home and there with be bologna sitting on the stairs. They&#39;ll leave their bag of trash outside their door for days. I&#39;ve tried talking to them however&#44; they don&#39;t speak english. How convienent. I&#39;ve reported them to the office several times but got the old &#34;haha we&#39;ll let them know.&#34;
I could be wrong but maybe THATS the source of the roaches???? I finally got them to put me on the list to be bombed. Asked them what I needed to do. All they said was take your clothes out of the closet and leave your cabinets open. If you have pets theyll need to stay out all day. I had school and I didn&#39;t have anywhere to put my cats so I rented a hotel room and had to pay for 2 days because I didn&#39;t get out of school until 4 30 and check out time is 12 pm. Well I get a call from my step mom saying that they didn&#39;t bomb because I didn&#39;t prepare correctly. I call them and ask them what the deal is and they said the bug man wouldn&#39;y do it b/c I didnt follow the directions on the sheet. What sheet? Ha&#44; the sheet they neglected to give me. They refuse to pay my hotel bill even though it was their fault. I schedule to be bombed the following week. And this time I have to skip school to make sure they do it. How sad is that? So I wait and wait and the bug guy never shows up. So I call the office&#44; &#34;oh&#44; um&#44; well&#44; um he&#39;ll be there soon hes still on the grounds. click.&#34; Bug man shows up and low and behold &#34;Hey yeah your name wasn&#39;t even on the list to be bombed. I had already finished and left and I had to come back to do your apt. Yeah the people in the office don&#39;t seem to have their ---- together.&#34;
2 months later&#44; I still have roaches. I finally got the guts to buy some bread and sandwhich meat to leave in the refridgerator. I just went to make some toast and about 4 huge roaches crawled out of my toaster after I turned it on. There is SO much more but I am going to be late for my doctor&#39;s appt. For some odd reason&#44; I can&#39;t figure it out&#44; but I keep getting sick.. I wonder why. Hmmm.
